 variety of themes connected with Jerusalem is held in late summer. Megalim Institute’s books and other publications have gained wide acclaim. They include both scientific works, such as Prof. Reich’s translation and redaction of Louis Vincent's Underground Jerusalem and more popular publications on the City of David and ancient Jerusalem. HomeMegalimConferencesCoursesSeminarsLibraryGalleryBooksContact.00awww.megalim.org.ildhttp://www.megalim.org.il/uhttp://www.megalim.org.il/00a-